@stage
Feature: Login To Presta shop

  Background: Prepare browser
    Given open chrome browser

  Scenario: Succesful login
    Given open http://demo.prestashop.com page
    When click LOGIN button
    Then we should see login form
    When enter 1001test@test.pl into email field
    And enter test1234 into password field
    And click SIGN_IN button
    Then we should see Your account message

  Scenario: Failed login wrong email
    Given open http://demo.prestashop.com page
    When click LOGIN button
    Then we should see login form
    When enter 2002test@test.pl into email field
    And enter test1234 into password field
    And click SIGN_IN button
    Then we should see Authentication failed. error alert